dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line): Taylor County, Wisconsin, 2016
dc_description_s: This data layer represents hydrography for Taylor County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase “Taylor_Hydro_2016.gdb”. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are “Taylor_HydroLine_2016” and “Taylor_HydroPoly_2016'. [HydroPoly: Water features such as Lakes, Reservoirs, Wide Streams and River, and Unspecified Open Water features.]
